{"type": "article", "id": 47324, "title": "Google 把断网的小彩蛋游戏搬到了线下，Papi 酱给洋码头拍广告 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-11-17T04:05:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25592, "name": "papi酱"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}, {"id": 3185, "name": "百事可乐"}, {"id": 45591, "name": "Havas"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171117103210Bnmt83TRQqSoLyEU.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #011480; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 14.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #011480; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #011480; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 14.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #011480; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #011480; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #323333} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #011480} span.s5 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24016.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Adidas neo 和快看漫画合作</b></a>，推出冬季漫画《零分偶像》番外篇和《当神不让》番外篇，漫画里的女主角是迪丽热巴。画风看起来有点一言难尽……<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711171050477WwSdiu5FgEjzAbq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.307813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24030.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">百事可乐和肯德基推出“你好 1987 上校百事可乐典藏罐”</a></b><strong>，</strong>这也是肯德基进驻中国 30 周年的营销之一。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171117112554kzTlvSXJtNpP6D5g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659420\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171117112612UTu4HEwyOkhW2nM1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.851563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/16/cpb-global-spokesperson/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>CPB 宣布英国女演员 Felicity Jones 将于 2018 年 1 月起担任品牌全球代言人</b></a>。Felicity Jones 曾因参演电影《万物理论》而获得奥斯卡金像奖、金球奖等多项提名。CPB 上一次任命全球首位代言人还要追溯到 2011 年，女星 Amanda Seyfried 被委任这一职责。中国市场方面，王珞丹作为 CPB 品牌好友近日拍摄了一支主题短片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017111711350065Ol3PiVW1cBaDxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.498413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23949.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了让你等红灯的时候有事干，Google 把 Chrome 浏览器断网时制作的小游戏搬到了线下</b></a>（就是那个一跳一跳的数码小恐龙）。可以说是非常 Geek 的消磨时间方式了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171117113804NGt9S8JEoly3mx2r.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.209375\" data-format=\"WEBP\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171117113709hXqvMFCcwEjtZSyH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.465625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/14/the-new-tvc-of-jimmy-choo/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>超模 Cara Delevingne 为 Jimmy Choo 拍摄 2018 早春系列短片</b></a>，相当撩人。</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0504b4me64&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/14/huawei-band-2-pro-we-train/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了在欧洲推广运动手环 Band 2 Pro，华为发布了全新营销活动 “We Train”</b></a>，广告展示了来自运动者和外卖员在同一时间的活动，通过比拼速度的镜头表现手环所具备的防水、独立 GPS 以及智能测算心率等功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o0504ilq7fv&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/tZoiKMUuDeolaD_30PaLOw\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Papi 酱最新的一条推送《三百六十行，行行出大夫》</b></a>，实际上是洋码头的黑五狂欢节广告。这支广告在腾讯视频上播放次数超过了 1.4 亿次。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z05055kc3a3&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://creativity-online.com/work/boots-show-them-you-know-them/53256\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国药妆连锁零售商 Boots 的圣诞广告讲了一段姐妹情</b></a>，背景音乐是 Only you。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=q0504368g4a&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/havas-shrinks-11-uk-unilever-pernod-ricard-cut-spend/1450462\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>由于客户联合利华和保乐力加减少了营销支出，法国广告集团 Havas 的第三季度财报不太乐观</b></a>，英国市场的有机收入下降了 10.9%，全球范围有机增长 0.1%，但集团营收下降了 2.2% 至 5.25 亿欧元。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23949.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">digitaling</a></p>"}